                        <interp inst="t18440506-name-486" type="given" value="JAMES"></interp>JAMES CUDDY</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable L</hi> 20.) I produce a certificate of Hill's former conviction, which I got from the Session-house of the borough of Kingston-on-Hull—(<hi rend="italic">read</hi>)—the prisoner is the man.</p>
